      <title>马杜罗请求友好委内瑞拉法庭核实其胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maduro-asks-friendly-venezuela-court-to-verify-his-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管反对派声称有证据证明总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗窃取了选票，但总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗仍要求委内瑞拉最高法院审计周日总统选举的结果，以证明其自我宣布的胜利合法化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/maduro-asks-friendly-venezuela-court-to-verify-his-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:36:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国考虑限制中国获取人工智能内存芯片</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-weighs-new-restrictions-on-china-s-access-to-ai-memory-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正考虑最早于下个月对中国获取人工智能存储芯片以及能够生产这些半导体的设备实施单方面限制，此举将进一步加剧世界最大经济体之间的技术竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-weighs-new-restrictions-on-china-s-access-to-ai-memory-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 17:41:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
