    <item>
      <title>Uber 和 Lyft 在纽约达成协议，减少司机被停职的情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/uber-and-lyft-strike-nyc-deal-to-scale-back-driver-lockouts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在优步和来福车同意控制司机停工现象后，纽约市官员收回了对这两家公司实施新的最低工资规定的威胁，最近的这一做法已导致部分司机的实得工资大幅下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/uber-and-lyft-strike-nyc-deal-to-scale-back-driver-lockouts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:56:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软业绩下滑后，Meta 投资者将重点关注资本支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/meta-investors-have-laser-focus-on-capex-after-microsoft-letdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 的投资者希望它能比微软公司和 Alphabet Inc. 更好地说服华尔街，在人工智能方面投入巨额资金是值得的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/meta-investors-have-laser-focus-on-capex-after-microsoft-letdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
